# Pacvue Design System

All UI work in this workspace must follow the design system defined in:
`pacvue-design-system/DESIGN.md`

## Core rules (enforce without exception)

- **Never hard-code brand colors** (`#FF9F43`, `#0253B6`). Always use `var(--pcv-brand)`.
- **Spacing**: 8px base grid only — use `4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 48px`. No 5px, 10px, 15px.
- **Border radius**: `4px` buttons/inputs · `6px` menu items · `8px` cards · `999px` chips. No other values.
- **Typography**: Inter only, minimum 11px, minimum weight 400. No font-weight 300.
- **Cards**: `border: 1px solid var(--pcv-border)` + `border-radius: var(--radius-lg)`. No box-shadow on flat cards.
- **Buttons**: `border-radius: var(--radius-sm)` (4px). Never pill-shaped.
- **Focus rings**: All interactive elements must have `outline: 2px solid var(--pcv-brand); outline-offset: 2px` on `:focus-visible`.

## Import order for new Vue projects

```js
// main.js / main.ts
import 'element-plus/dist/index.css'
import '@/../../pacvue-design-system/tokens.css'      // or copy to project
import '@/../../pacvue-design-system/el-overrides.css'
```

## Theme switching

```html
<!-- Blue theme (default) -->
<html data-theme="blue">

<!-- Orange theme -->
<html data-theme="orange">
```

## Quick token reference

```
Brand:        var(--pcv-brand)           Nav bg:   var(--pcv-nav-bg)
Hover bg:     var(--pcv-hover-bg)        Selected: var(--pcv-selected-bg)
Success:      var(--pcv-success)         Warning:  var(--pcv-warning)
Error:        var(--pcv-error)           Link:     var(--pcv-link)
Text primary: var(--pcv-text-primary)   Surface:  var(--pcv-surface)
Border:       var(--pcv-border)          Page bg:  var(--pcv-bg)
```

## Responsive breakpoints

| Width | Role |
|-------|------|
| 1280px | Minimum supported |
| 1440px | **Primary design target** — build all designs at this width |
| 1920px | Apply `max-width: var(--content-max-width)` on `.page-content` |

Full reference: `pacvue-design-system/DESIGN.md`
